Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.28,0:02:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's a good girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.95,0:02:27.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Grow, grow bigger and leave\Nthe scars of your flames behind.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.35,0:02:51.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,One more... One more and this night\Nbefore the carnival will be concluded.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:58.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the beginning of the flames\Nthat will light up this stinkin' town.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.90,0:03:03.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The beginning of the beautiful carnival.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.25,0:03:16.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.80,0:03:18.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.88,0:03:19.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.01,0:03:21.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.13,0:03:21.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:37.65,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story 3
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.56,0:03:37.65,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part 1)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.31,0:03:36.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story 3. Part 1!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.11,0:03:40.57,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Police station
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.20,0:03:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.82,0:03:45.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And what did that man's eyes look like?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.20,0:03:51.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hmm, they were like the eyes of a fox,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.71,0:03:54.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,THIS sharp.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.33,0:03:56.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The eyes were slanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.46,0:04:00.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, was he something like this?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.34,0:04:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nothing like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.22,0:04:04.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.47,0:04:06.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're really bad at drawing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.22,0:04:08.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's practically a child's doodle.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.97,0:04:10.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't there anyone better?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's nothing I can do!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.60,0:04:15.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who draws faces,\NTomokawa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, has a cold and is absent today.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.40,0:04:18.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Excuse me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.07,0:04:21.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.15,0:04:22.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.36,0:04:28.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't expect to give this\Npicture to the investigations department.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.24,0:04:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I do think it has a surreal and noteworthy style though.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.46,0:04:34.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.67,0:04:38.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why don't you two draw one instead of me then?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.63,0:04:41.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh... N-No, pictures aren't exactly...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.76,0:04:44.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My specialty is impressionist painting, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.59,0:04:46.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,H-Hey wait, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.72,0:04:48.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez, he plays dirty.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.30,0:04:55.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, and we aren't even certain that the\Nman she saw really was the arson culprit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.77,0:04:59.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that? Are you trying\Nto say that Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r} is lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:02.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if she's a kid, you should still take her seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.74,0:05:08.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But you didn't see the man lighting\Nthe fire with your own eyes, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.07,0:05:09.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.24,0:05:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On these hot days,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.95,0:05:15.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A man wearing a long trench coat with leather gloves,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.12,0:05:19.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Letting off the scent of lamp oil all\Nover his pants where he spilled it,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.71,0:05:23.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Walking out from a back alley near the\Nplace the fire broke out with a sickening grin,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.42,0:05:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't it be harder to say that he isn't the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.18,0:05:29.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.22,0:05:33.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it was. Right, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.23,0:05:38.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, either way, let's go to that back alley.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:40.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And analyze the scene of the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.23,0:05:42.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Analyzing the scene of the crime?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.73,0:05:44.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright!\NThen I'll come as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.99,0:05:47.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, we can take my car.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.53,0:05:51.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sure, but I'm going to stop by somewhere first.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.03,0:05:53.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's on the way there so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.45,0:05:55.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Stop by somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.79,0:05:58.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is a special day for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.67,0:06:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Special day?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.88,0:06:02.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is it your birthday?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.21,0:06:04.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.42,0:06:06.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the opposite.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.84,0:06:07.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Opposite?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.72,0:06:17.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I wonder where she's gonna stop at?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.39,0:06:20.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A special day, huh...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:40.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! I remember now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.13,0:06:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Today is the day Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father,\NOfficer Satou Masayoshi, passed away.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.38,0:06:48.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The day her father died on duty.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.55,0:06:50.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, really?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.93,0:06:51.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.05,0:06:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Exactly 18 years ago today.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.68,0:06:58.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While chasing a killer robber, at this intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.64,0:07:00.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At this intersection?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.27,0:07:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, he got hit by a truck at this intersection.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.02,0:07:10.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, there was a heavy\Nstorm that day, and the ambulance was late.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.70,0:07:16.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In the ambulance, under the eyes of\NSatou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and her family, he drew his last breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:18.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what Inspector Megure told me.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.12,0:07:22.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I recall, the name of the case is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.71,0:07:24.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shuushirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.92,0:07:27.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, Shuushirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.01,0:07:28.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Shuushirou.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:33.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After the officer was hit by the\Ntruck, as the criminal ran away,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.09,0:07:39.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He repeatedly called out that mysterious name.\NThus the case was named the "Shuushirou case."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.14,0:07:44.10,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shuushirou Case
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.18,0:07:43.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At the time, they even did a house to house search.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.69,0:07:49.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But the officer they believed to\Nhave held the key to the case was dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.78,0:07:53.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the investigation remained unsolved, and\Nthree years ago the statute of limitations expired.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.91,0:07:58.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, that's what Uncle Kogorou said.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.79,0:08:02.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, I've seen that case a lot\Nof times on TV, so I know it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.66,0:08:04.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was close...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.83,0:08:12.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It was a flawless heist, and the only clue left\Nbehind was the security tape of about 10 seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.84,0:08:20.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even how the officer who died on duty managed to\Ndetermine who the culprit is, still remains a mystery.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.10,0:08:26.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I never knew that officer was Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s father.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be helped.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.36,0:08:33.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if the name of the case and the\Noffender's name remain on the record,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.65,0:08:36.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Something like the name of a\Nofficer who died while on a case,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.16,0:08:43.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Isn't something anyone remembers\Nunless they are police officers themselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.29,0:08:44.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sa-Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.12,0:08:50.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we aren't doing this\Njob to be remembered anyways.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.51,0:08:56.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, didn't that truck driver see the culprit's face?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.43,0:09:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He said the culprit was wearing a long rain coat,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.76,0:09:02.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So he couldn't even tell if it was a male or female.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.18,0:09:08.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even in the image of the security camera, he\Nwas wearing a hat, a mask, sunglasses, and a coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.81,0:09:11.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he knew the culprit's name,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.90,0:09:13.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That "Shuushirou?"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.65,0:09:19.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of the people who were called with\Nthat name was capable of committing the crime.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.58,0:09:22.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess it was bound to be unsolved.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.04,0:09:29.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If the clues were the security\Ntape, the rain coat, and "Shuushirou,"
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.42,0:09:30.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There are four.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.46,0:09:40.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The fourth clue is three letters written in\NKatakana in his police notebook "ka-n-o."
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.31,0:09:42.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kano?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.81,0:09:44.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is the first time I've heard of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.31,0:09:48.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hear that the police was trying to keep it classified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.65,0:09:53.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,According to reports nationwide, it\Nappears to have had a lot to do with the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.82,0:09:59.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they asked my mother and I so many times if\Nwe have heard of my father saying anything about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.12,0:10:01.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.83,0:10:03.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not only have I never heard of it,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.33,0:10:05.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have no clue as to what it means.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.20,0:10:10.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was a kid, I always used to always\Nthink as I stared at those three syllables.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.67,0:10:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That I would grant any wish of the person\Nwho solves this mystery and catches Shuushirou!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.05,0:10:20.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Any...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.93,0:10:22.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wish...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.68,0:10:27.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If I get it, would you buy me\Na thousand Unajuu rice bowls?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.06,0:10:28.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:32.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I want to live in the castle at Tropical Land.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.36,0:10:36.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I would like an entrance pass\Nto the international space station.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.49,0:10:39.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I would like a name-brand bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:43.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Would a ticket to the next world cup for me be alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.12,0:10:45.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,S-Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.04,0:10:48.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only these kids take it so realistically that it's scary.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.71,0:10:51.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's up with you two?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.13,0:10:59.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Flowers...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.76,0:11:05.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's been quite a while!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.89,0:11:09.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Aren't you Miwa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.02,0:11:10.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've grown up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.27,0:11:12.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know them?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.60,0:11:15.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, they're members of father's\Nbaseball club from when he was in high school.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.07,0:11:20.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my father's battery-mate,\Nthe ace, Saruwatari Hiderou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.82,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Saruwatari Hiderou (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.86,0:11:21.82,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Highschool teacher
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.86,0:11:21.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nice to meet you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.41,0:11:25.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Famous for his strong arm and swift legs,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.62,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kano Shyuuji (49)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.70,0:11:28.62,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Italian restaurant manager
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.37,0:11:27.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kano Shyuuji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.99,0:11:28.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.50,0:11:30.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The team's dependable slugger,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.38,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Financial company president
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.87,0:11:34.38,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Inomata Mitsuo (50)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.46,0:11:32.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inomata Mitsuo{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.17,0:11:38.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the beautiful manager, Kandori Chyouko{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:41.34,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Kandori Chyouko (49)
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.84,0:11:41.34,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Boutique owner
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.55,0:11:41.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh stop it, I'm a 50 year-old grandmother now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.72,0:11:44.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What are you all doing here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.14,0:11:46.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We've decided to all have a drink together.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.31,0:11:52.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But first, we came to greet the captain, Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.73,0:11:54.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.06,0:11:57.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If we didn't greet him, then\Nwe would have gotten depressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.11,0:12:04.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We'll be at the usual bar, so you should come to join us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.45,0:12:03.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.95,0:12:06.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Inspector Megure.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.49,0:12:08.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.33,0:12:12.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right now we're in Haido-city, fourth district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.54,0:12:16.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, someone spotted a suspicious\Ncharacter who might be the arson culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.92,0:12:21.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, the location is Shinagawa, sixth district.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:26.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While the men on patrol were in the\Nmiddle of questioning him, the man fled.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.30,0:12:27.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Currently we're in pursuit.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.93,0:12:29.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The man's characteristics are...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.72,0:12:32.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Long hair with a hat and a grey coat.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.77,0:12:34.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's close to where you guys are.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.69,0:12:40.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Leave the kids with Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, and\Nyou and Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} go back them up.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.32,0:12:42.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's what he said.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.94,0:12:43.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Let's go, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.07,0:12:45.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.33,0:12:50.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong? Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.74,0:12:56.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh, Police notebook, handgun and...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.92,0:12:58.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Crap! Not good...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.88,0:12:59.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.21,0:13:04.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I left my handcuffs on the desk at the station.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.30,0:13:07.89,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,We don't have time to go back and...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.39,0:13:10.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You alright, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.56,0:13:14.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No problem, as for handcuffs, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} still has his.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.89,0:13:19.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And according to the magazine\Nfortune teller, I'm super lucky today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.86,0:13:23.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So even without handcuffs, handling that criminal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.32,0:13:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dear, be careful, alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.70,0:13:32.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, according to the\Nfortune teller, I'm super lucky today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.45,0:13:36.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Huh, dad forgot his handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.84,0:13:40.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What, my husband?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.00,0:13:42.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My husband? By a car...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.05,0:13:44.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And where is he right now?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.55,0:13:52.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This isn't right. Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:55.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Dad, you're on the good guy's side.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.81,0:13:57.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're working hard for justice.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.35,0:13:59.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.98,0:14:07.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You idiot. The word "justice" is... The word "justice" is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.57,0:14:08.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.53,0:14:09.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.49,0:14:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you alright?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.95,0:14:16.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, we'll be off now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.66,0:14:18.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll leave the kids with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.87,0:14:20.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.54,0:14:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait a second, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.92,0:14:23.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.71,0:14:24.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.02,0:14:42.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're pretty rusty, these handcuffs.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.86,0:14:45.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you don't have handcuffs, please take these.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.15,0:14:47.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah... Alright.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.99,0:14:50.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They're a memento of my father.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.41,0:14:59.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I broke mine during the Higashida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Ncase, so I've been using them for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.33,0:15:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It should be perfect as a charm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.17,0:15:05.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Cha-Charm...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.30,0:15:07.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Didn't your father die while on duty?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.05,0:15:09.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just take them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.72,0:15:11.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Be careful, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.38,0:15:12.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Sa-Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.80,0:15:12.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:12.59,0:15:13.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, y-yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.35,0:15:17.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.27,0:15:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's that all about?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.90,0:15:29.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bringing a gun just to catch an arson suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.61,0:15:34.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And they're investigators for violent criminals.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.24,0:15:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Shouldn't arson be investigated by a different division?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.04,0:15:39.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A stab victim was found.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.75,0:15:42.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Near the 4th combustion site.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.17,0:15:46.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not positive, but he either witnessed the arson,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.34,0:15:49.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Or was stabbed when he tried to stop the culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.42,0:15:51.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So that's why we're moving too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.47,0:15:55.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, don't move away from my side.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.02,0:16:10.49,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Shinagawa Station
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.40,0:16:13.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, this is Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.99,0:16:18.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, we've apprehended the suspicious\Ncharacter who fled questioning at Shinagawa station.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.91,0:16:20.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not me!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.00,0:16:26.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he's saying that he's not the\Narson culprit and just a regular thief.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.96,0:16:31.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it! That's what it was!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.34,0:16:33.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I solved the mystery!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.09,0:16:35.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I am lucky today!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.05,0:16:37.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Alright, time to give Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.72,0:16:38.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.23,0:16:46.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, where are you calling?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.81,0:16:49.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uhh... Nowhere...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.82,0:16:52.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.40,0:16:54.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uh, where was...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.37,0:16:59.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, yeah, this one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.12,0:17:04.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When I was getting Kamen Yaiba\Ngashapon here, a weird man came out of there.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.17,0:17:13.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello, this is Satou.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.26,0:17:17.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, how was that suspicious character?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:22.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?! You know who the\Nculprit is in the case 18 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.02,0:17:28.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, if my deductions are correct, it's probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.98,0:17:31.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please don't be surprised... It probably is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.86,0:17:33.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The culprit was among the people we met today.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:35.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person is...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.28,0:17:40.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What is it, Shiratori{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.87,0:17:44.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, there's\Nsomething strange about your behavior.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.54,0:17:48.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come on, give me a break...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.47,0:18:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah. That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.22,0:18:04.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I understand everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.18,0:18:07.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The true meaning of Shuushirou,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.44,0:18:08.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And the mystery of Kano,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.19,0:18:15.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And how your father was able\Nto determine who the culprit was.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.24,0:18:17.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I got all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.32,0:18:21.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Although the statute of limitations has passed already.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.91,0:18:23.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, who is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.08,0:18:25.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Who's the culprit?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.96,0:18:29.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, the culprit is...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.76,0:18:42.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey! Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:43.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.72,0:18:48.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.31,0:18:50.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.98,0:18:52.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's wrong?! Answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.49,0:19:00.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, answer me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.74,0:19:03.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.91,0:19:08.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hello?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.21,0:19:15.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.13,0:19:18.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I'll leave the rest to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.76,0:19:25.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, this is Shiratori.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.26,0:19:27.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, Satou{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.97,0:19:30.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I've just sent that suspicious\Ncharacter to the Shinagawa department.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.56,0:19:33.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eh? Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.73,0:19:37.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yes, he was with me until 4-5 minutes ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.44,0:19:42.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then please send his last known location\Nand time to the station command center.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.86,0:19:44.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was attacked by someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.03,0:19:46.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Just now, while on the phone with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.29,0:19:50.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The attacker might be that\Narson culprit as well, so be careful!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:56.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Officer Takagi was attacked when he was telling you\Nabout who the culprit in the case 18 years ago was, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.38,0:19:58.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then the culprit would be...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.17,0:20:00.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.05,0:20:03.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That case was prescribed 3 years ago,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.84,0:20:07.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And there's no way of knowing if\NTakagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s deductions are right or wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.85,0:20:10.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, those four we met this afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:12.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,They said they were going to go to the usual bar to drink,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.23,0:20:14.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.73,0:20:15.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.86,0:20:19.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the tavern is Nanamagari.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.24,0:20:24.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The location is... In front of Shinagawa station...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.49,0:20:32.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In that last call, if Detective Takagi\Nsaid that the culprit is in one of those four,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.92,0:20:38.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And if one of those four just happened to hear\Nthe phone conversation in front of Shinagawa station,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.42,0:20:44.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then there is a chance that the culprit\Nattacked Detective Takagi to keep his mouth shut.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:50.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In any case, I'm going to Shinagawa station.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.39,0:20:52.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So you guys take the train and go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.39,0:20:54.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Come back to the department tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.44,0:21:01.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If there's a chance that the one who\Nattacked Detective Takagi could be the arson culprit,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.03,0:21:07.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then I think there is no other choice but to\Nbring Yoshida{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, who is the only eye-witness.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.37,0:21:09.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.37,0:21:10.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.58,0:21:11.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.41,0:21:12.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll assist, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.96,0:21:14.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Geez.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.67,0:21:24.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bulletin from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:25.26,0:21:26.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To all officers in the Shinagawa area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.88,0:21:28.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Location: Near Shinagawa station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.10,0:21:30.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Condition: Unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.68,0:21:32.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A member of police has been attacked by someone,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.93,0:21:34.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Possibly heavily injured.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:35.27,0:21:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Immediate investigation is top priority.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.15,0:21:37.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I repeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.44,0:21:39.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Bulletin from headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.81,0:21:41.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To all officers in the Shinagawa area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.27,0:21:43.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Location: Near Shinagawa station.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.24,0:21:51.03,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A lie, it's got to be a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.37,0:21:57.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one was among one of those four...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.21,0:22:00.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one who killed my dad.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.43,0:22:14.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That can't be right... Dad?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:24.53,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Natsu no maboroshi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.98,0:22:24.53,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Garnet Crow
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:37.16,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Heya no mado no mukou ni hikouki kumo o nazotte
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.91,0:22:37.16,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Beyond the window I see a trace\Nof clouds made by an airplane
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:45.42,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Kyou kenkashita kimi no koto bakari kangaeteta
Dialogue: 0,0:22:38.04,0:22:45.42,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,And realize I can only think about the fight we had today
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.89,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Sasai na koto de to madotte fuantei de muboubi na
Dialogue: 0,0:22:47.97,0:22:55.89,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I hesitate with every small thing,\Nand I'm unreliable and hopeless,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:04.11,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Ano koro no you ni sugu ni denwashite\Nwarai aetara ii no ni ne
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.18,0:23:04.11,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Wishing to be able to be like I used to,\Nand call you right away, laughing
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:14.87,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Chika zuite kuru shifuku no toki wa\Nitami o tomonainagara ashi oto o tateru
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.40,0:23:14.87,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I can hear the steps of happiness coming\Ncloser, bringing pain along with it
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:23.67,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Kangaesugite fukami ni hamaru kimi no soba ni iru no ni
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.91,0:23:23.67,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,You are so focused in deep thoughts you\Ndon't realize I'm right beside you
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:32.47,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Natsu no maboroshi hitomi tojimete ichiban saishou ni kimi o omoidasu yo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.67,0:23:32.47,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,Summer illusions I see, closing my eyes\Nthe first one I remember is you,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.72,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Dakedo kimi to ikiteyukitai kara
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.76,0:23:36.72,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,And it's because I want to live with you by my side
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:42.35,Dialogue Top,ED JP,0,0,0,,Tomadoinagara demo ii tsunaida te o hanasanaide ne
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.97,0:23:42.35,Dialogue,ED EN,0,0,0,,I don't mind if you hesitate, just never let go of my hand
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.02,0:24:09.30,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Next Episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.73,0:23:49.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That person! That's the person!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.03,0:23:51.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the bad man I saw!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.07,0:23:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Those kids aren't here!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.99,0:23:58.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There, now you can see better, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.87,0:24:01.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then does that mean the one\Nwho attacked Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} was...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:01.79,0:24:03.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,DAMN IT!!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:03.67,0:24:09.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Now then, shall we have a drink to celebrate... Kano{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:15.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story 3
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.30,0:24:15.01,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,(Part 2)
Dialogue: 0,0:24:09.88,0:24:11.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.30,0:24:14.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Metropolitan Police Detective Love Story 3. Part 2!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:15.89,0:24:18.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.68,0:24:19.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Romaji.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.02,0:24:25.06,Signs,Sign,0,0,0,,Please anticipate our next episode!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.48,0:24:21.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next time is the solution!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.81,0:24:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Takagi, I'm a police officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.85,0:24:24.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were done for?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:24.06,0:24:24.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah... AHHH!!
